# Public API (pa:*)
  @api pa.computeDesired(bindings)  @ 90-122
      -- Pure: bindings -> { [trackGuid] = trackSpec }. Pooled duplicates collapse
      -- via the seen-keys; slot order is sorted for a stable REAPER image.
  @api pa.frecencyOrder(params, fxScores)  @ 291-304
      @contract  pure, stable: decayed score desc, then param index; fxScores may be nil  @ 290
  @api pa:apply()  @ 309-323
      @contract  no-op (and no undo point) when every track's mirror already matches  @ 308
  @api pa:automate(chan, target)  @ 326-343
      @contract  chan is the tracker's 1-based channel; returns the allocated cc lane, or nil + reason  @ 325
  @api pa:unautomate(chan, lane)  @ 345-352
  @api pa:binding(chan, lane)  @ 354-357
  @api pa:targets()  @ 360-365
