  @api pa:params(trackGuid, fxGuid)  @ 368-389
      @contract  cached per fxGuid (param-count change invalidates); frecency-hot params first  @ 367
  @api pa:bumpFrecency(trackGuid, fxGuid, paramIndex)  @ 392-406
      @contract  advances the ident's use counter; the param's score decays to it, then +1  @ 391
  @api pa:floatFx(trackGuid, fxGuid)  @ 409-414
      @contract  floats the fx ui; true only when pa floated it — caller owns popping it down  @ 408
  @api pa:unfloatFx(trackGuid, fxGuid)  @ 416-419
  @api pa:lastTouched()  @ 422-431
      @contract  last-touched track-fx param as guids + name; nil for take/container/input fx  @ 421

